oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Cedarwood Publishing Co. Artists with Curley Rhodes Quote (with signature)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Autographs; Cedarwood Publishing Company; Offset printing; Rhodes, Curly;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: One color offset printing plate (red on silver) advertising songs by Cedarwood Publishing Company artists. The printing plate features a quote by Curley Rhodes and his signature. The plate also features photographs of Webb Pierce, Ray Price, Ernest Tubb, Carl Smith, Stonewall Jackson, Jerry Wallace, Max Powell, Wayne Walker, Mel Tillis, Bobby Sykes, Bobbi Staff, and Bobbie Martin.
